62. Nieman Kristin M., Romero Iris L., Van Houten Bennett, Lengyel Ernst. Adipose tissue and adipocytes support tumorigenesis and metastasis. Biochimica et Biophysica Acta (BBA) - Molecular and Cell Biology of Lipids. 2013;1831(10):1533–1541. doi: 10.1016/j.bbalip.2013.02.010. [PMC free article] [PubMed] [CrossRef] [Google Scholar]

