Figure 11
Mode of inhibition by compound 16.
The Lineweaver–Burk plots indicate that compound 16 is competitive with respect to DXP (A) and competitive with respect to NADPH (B). All assays were performed in duplicate using purified Y. pestis MEP synthase. The enzyme was not preincubated with compound 16, in contrast to Figure 12.

